{"tid":100671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禁穆斯林惹禍】星巴克出招對抗特朗普 將聘一萬難民","createTime":"2017-01-30T08:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T13:22:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41ad78a66b6c0689e00755eb4e6424577d9ba2a3","tid":100671,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:23:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170130/56240022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170130%2F56240022&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=28552ebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170130%2F56240022&h=98ae7409\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170130/56240022</a> <br />\n<br />\n【禁穆斯林惹禍】星巴克出招對抗特朗普 將聘一萬難民<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0130 12:39<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170130/large/1485742181_2ac3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170130%2Flarge%2F1485742181_2ac3.jpg&h=038c04a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普簽署行政禁令，無限期停止接收難民及禁止七個穆斯林國家旅客入境。國際連鎖咖啡店星巴克出招對抗，宣佈未來5年聘請1萬名難民；而矽谷一眾科企周末亦群起反抗移民政策，宣佈為受影響員工提供法律支援。<br />\n<br />\n星巴克行政總裁舒爾茨（Howard Schultz）周日在一封寫給員工的信中表示，全球分店未來未來5年將聘請1萬名難民。<br />\n<br />\n他與特朗普主張的政策唱反調，表明支援墨西哥種植咖啡豆的農夫，又強調如果「奧巴馬醫保」被推翻，公司會向合資格員工提供醫療保險。<br />\n<br />\n依賴移民專才的矽谷亦反對新政，大企業如蘋果、Google及微軟等，向受行政命令影響的員工提供法援，有幾位科企高層更私人捐款，支援移民員工。<br />\n<br />\nTesla行政總裁馬斯克（Elon Musk）及Uber行政總裁卡蘭尼克（Travis Kalanick）已加入特朗普的商業諮詢委員會，他們在Twitter表示會在委員會中表達業界的憂慮。<br />\n美聯社／路透社"},{"pid":"ec6ec58732efab7a89660cd386c61eaef0f0d18d","tid":100671,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df4706fe00f1e4a08c5d6db3e56bd963efd5d82c","tid":100671,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e35c306d2c3434dc9bfa3ad665997e22fb2a9e","tid":100671,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:35:15.000Z","msg":"點解左膠生存到今日都仲咁撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a21a8217246641ffd4c65eee332309c715c7d9","tid":100671,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"笑死人 呢d跨國剝削企業突然間變成大愛左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fe9714a80ba481dc03b6ba6498d1115ca8e98c","tid":100671,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0898705100eade7ecfb6baa0ffec61ee17367705","tid":100671,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑死人 呢d跨國剝削企業突然間變成大愛左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55812b296eb875b30094b848cdecbfb1a7fec9db","tid":100671,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>難民人工平啊<br />\n講到咁正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正想講<br />\n全部都係仆街食屎狗<br />\n假到冇內有"},{"pid":"e15de37fe0df9085297f0bad11e9df380d5e89ce","tid":100671,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:40:47.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c816d18c75f2987d3f6d094b7390f1df3119ab5","tid":100671,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"<b