政命令影響的員工提供法援，有幾位科企高層更私人捐款，支援移民員工。<br />\n<br />\nTesla行政總裁馬斯克（Elon Musk）及Uber行政總裁卡蘭尼克（Travis Kalanick）已加入特朗普的商業諮詢委員會，他們在Twitter表示會在委員會中表達業界的憂慮。<br />\n美聯社／路透社</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚好點解唔係 obama care 前提供。左膠左上腦重要引清兵入關。<br />\n本來難民就唔係本地人，你重要背叛自己人走去請難民？<br />\n又係一班寧與外人不讓家奴既狗賊，你唔撚請難民入你屋企住？"},{"pid":"4787865894842c9f54aee84fcb2cc8771f26579b","tid":100671,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解左膠生存到今日都仲咁撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到佢地屋企人俾難民輪姦個陣睇佢地仲左唔左"},{"pid":"cb897effdb7b400a44843dfff598d92b7f49c89e","tid":100671,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170130/56240022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170130%2F56240022&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=28552ebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170130%2F56240022&h=98ae7409\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170130/56240022</a> <br />\n<br />\n【禁穆斯林惹禍】星巴克出招對抗特朗普 將聘一萬難民<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0130 12:39<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170130/large/1485742181_2ac3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170130%2Flarge%2F1485742181_2ac3.jpg&h=038c04a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普簽署行政禁令，無限期停止接收難民及禁止七個穆斯林國家旅客入境。國際連鎖咖啡店星巴克出招對抗，宣佈未來5年聘請1萬名難民；而矽谷一眾科企周末亦群起反抗移民政策，宣佈為受影響員工提供法律支援。<br />\n<br />\n星巴克行政總裁舒爾茨（Howard Schultz）周日在一封寫給員工的信中表示，全球分店未來未來5年將聘請1萬名難民。<br />\n<br />\n他與特朗普主張的政策唱反調，表明支援墨西哥種植咖啡豆的農夫，<span style=\"color: red;\">又強調如果「奧巴馬醫保」被推翻，公司會向合資格員工提供醫療保險。</span><br />\n<br />\n依賴移民專才的矽谷亦反對新政，大企業如蘋果、Google及微軟等，向受行政命令影響的員工提供法援，有幾位科企高層更私人捐款，支援移民員工。<br />\n<br />\nTesla行政總裁馬斯克（Elon Musk）及Uber行政總裁卡蘭尼克（Travis Kalanick）已加入特朗普的商業諮詢委員會，他們在Twitter表示會在委員會中表達業界的憂慮。<br />\n美聯社／路透社</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚好點解唔係 obama care 前提供。左膠左上腦重要引清兵入關。<br />\n本來難民就唔係本地人，你重要背叛自己人走去請難民？<br />\n又係一班寧與外人不讓家奴既狗賊，你唔撚請難民入你屋企住？</blockquote><br />\n其實係咪侵侵黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e69f1244f82636f61fd9a2770605590e7b7a6c9","tid":100671,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:51:30.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 想d難民強姦d staff? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb5045a1feb8c24bbc882dbca04f5420a7fd91b","tid":100671,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"花生"},{"pid":"9b79431a57d3345d5fd084dd44136d6ab2d233d5","tid":100671,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170130/56240022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170130%2F56240022&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=28552ebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170130%2F56240022&h=98ae7409\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170130/56240022</a> <br />\n<br />\n【禁穆斯林惹禍】星巴克出招對抗特朗普 將聘一萬難民<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0130 12:39<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170130/large/1485742181_2ac3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170130%2Flarge%2F1485742181_2ac3.